Delete Multiple Records
Use a WHERE clause that matches more than one row to delete many records at once.

Example:
DELETE FROM Customers
WHERE Country = 'Mexico';

What this does:
This query deletes all rows in the Customers table where the Country value is Mexico.

Result after delete:
